key_risks: Intense competition from established players and emerging technologies
Revenue growth deceleration and stock price volatility
High customer concentration increasing vulnerability to churn
Sensitivity to macroeconomic downturns impacting IT spending
controversies: Trade secret litigation, including a settlement with Redis Labs in 2020
environmental_issues: Limited progress metrics on energy-efficient data management solutions
social_issues: Limited exposure to privacy regulations due to not catering to children
governance_issues: Potential risks to intellectual property from legal disputes
